> *****************************************************************************
> ***
> * Description *
> /*
> This file cleans the CDE staff demographics files. The combined dataset is
> unique on districtcode, year, and recid.
> 
> Data Location: https://www.cde.ca.gov/ds/ad/staffdemo.asp
> */
> *****************************************************************************
> ***
> 
> *****************************************************
