. /*---------------------------------------------------------------------------
> ---
> do/data_prep/schl_chars/clean_sch_char.do — Phase 1a §3.3 step 9 batch 9b rel
> ocation
> =============================================================================
> ===
> 
> PURPOSE
>     MASTER assembly: merges 6 sister-cleaner tempfiles + 4 chain dtas; produc
> es $datadir_clean/sch_char.dta.
> 
> INVOKED FROM
>     `do/main.do' Phase 1 (DATA PREP) under flag `do_data_prep'.
> 
> INPUTS (verified via grep on file body)
>     $consolidated_dir/do/va/helpers/macros_va.doh  (consolidated helper)
>     $datadir_clean/cde/charter_status.dta  (CHAIN read; from this batch)
>     $datadir_clean/cde/ecn_disadv.dta  (CHAIN read; from this batch)
>     $datadir_clean/cde/elsch/elsch_`spring_year'_clean.dta  (CHAIN read; from
>  this batch)
