> 
> 
> // check the schools in the VA base sample not merged to the distance dataset
> 
> /*
> do $consolidated_dir/do/data_prep/k12_postsec_distance/check_merge.do
> 
>  */
> 
> * --- output-directory prep (CANONICAL) -------------------------------------
> --
