> RELOCATION (per plan v3 §3.3 step 9 batch 9d, applied 2026-05-08)
>     Source: caschls/do/build/prepare/poolgr11enr.do
>     Path repointing applied (script-based methodology):
>       $projdir/log/build/prepare/*                    -> $logdir/*  (CANONICA
> L)
>       $projdir/dta/enrollment/schoollevel/* (read OR write) -> $datadir_clean
> /enrollment/schoollevel/*  (CANONICAL chain)
>       $projdir/dta/enrollment/raw/* (read)             -> $caschls_projdir/dt
> a/enrollment/raw/*  (LEGACY raw)
