> ).
.     * Reads CHAIN $datadir_clean/calschls/<sub>/<x><year>.dta (from renamedat
> a batch 9d).
.     * Writes CHAIN $datadir_clean/calschls/qoiclean/<sub>/<x>qoiclean<year>.d
> ta.
